data.description: Public Remarks:  (576 characters) THE HOME OF YOUR DREAMS! White picket fence, rocking chair front porch, and tons of space are only the start for this beautiful home on a FULL FINISHED basement!! Walking inside you’re greeted by beautiful HW floors, formal dining room, and living room with FP overlooked by the cozy kitchen with all new light fixtures, island, and breakfast area! Continuing through you’ll find 2 spacious guest rooms with brand new carpet, and the Master Suite is HUGE with an en-suite bathroom fully renovated. It includes new separate tub/shower, double vanities, toilet, flooring, his/hers closets, everything! Oh yes, did I mention SPACE, downstairs you’ll find a den, 2 more huge guest rooms with walk in closets, new floors and plenty of storage. This amazing property also features a screened in back porch with A/C and FP for all occasions! Big screen doors showcase the fenced in backyard with a doghouse and garden including fig tree, wisteria, japanese maple, and much more! We’re not done yet! The home also a separate 20x20 building with A/C, which can serve as a workshop, guest room, you name it! This home is on a first come first serve basis so book your showing today!!
